OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBelfast Trust says sorry   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover contaminated blood    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Belfast Health Trust has apologised to 
OL,6, people infected and affected by        
OL,7, contaminated blood products.           
OL,9,FAt the the public inquiry into the     
OL,10,FUK-wide infected blood scandal, the    
OL,11,Ftrust said it it recognised the harm,  
OL,12,Fhurt and distress that had been caused.
OL,14,FUp to 30,000 people were given         
OL,15,Fcontaminated blood in the 1970s and    
OL,16,F1980s.                                 
OL,18,FIt has been called the biggest         
OL,19,Ftreatment disaster in NHS history.     
